            <title><![CDATA[Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds ‘Puyo Puyo Content Drop’ update launches May 27]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/sonic-racing-crossworlds-puyo-puyo-content-drop-update-launches-may-27</link>
            <guid>1530616</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>The “<em>Puyo Puyo</em> Content Drop” update for <em>Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds</em> will launch on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20260528T0000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">May 27 at 5:00 p.m. PT / 8:00 p.m. ET</a>, SEGA <a href="https://x.com/CrossWorldsJPN/status/2059409245032915304" target="_blank" rel="noopener">announced</a>. <span id="more-1050064"></span></p><p>The update will include the following content:</p><ul><li>Arle from <em>Puyo Puyo</em> as a playable character</li><li>Twinkle Bayoen vehicle</li></ul><p>An in-game “<em>Puyo Puyo</em> Festival” will also run from <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20260529T0000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">May 28 at 5:00 p.m. PT / 8:00 p.m. ET</a> until <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20260531T2359" target="_blank" rel="noopener">May 31 at 4:59 pm. PT / 7:59 p.m. ET</a>.</p><p><em><a title="Games > Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds [26 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sonic-racing-crossworlds">Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds</a></em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2486820/Sonic_Racing_CrossWorlds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/sonic-racing-crossworlds" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/sonic-racing-crossworlds-puyo-puyo-content-drop-update-launches-may-27]]></content:encoded>
